Elephants are very big animals and have a long memory and also have a very long nose called a trunk. They make a trumpet sound.
The lion is the king of the jungle, he roars loud!
Monkeys spend a lot of time up in trees, they like to eat fruits. Carl is a monkey and has a banana.
Kolin is a kangaroo from Australia. He bounces and bounces anywhere it wants to go.
Giraffes have a very long neck to reach the tender leaves up high on a tree. They are very tall and very quiet animals.
